Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.55,0:02:16.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奇形…
Dialogue: 9,0:02:14.90,0:02:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mutants…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:42.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,村に１人の少年が住んでいた
Dialogue: 9,0:02:38.93,0:02:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There lived a boy in the village.{rep}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.55,0:02:51.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とても そうめいな子だったが
Dialogue: 9,0:02:49.10,0:02:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a boy of great intelligence, but he had one weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:54.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１つの欠点があった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:56.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,瞬！ あっ…
Dialogue: 9,0:02:54.57,0:02:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun!
Dialogue: 9,0:02:59.49,0:03:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Solitude was his only friend and confidant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:03.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,孤独だけが 彼の友達となり\N話し相手に…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:12.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少年は知らず知らずのうちに\N業を積み重ね
Dialogue: 9,0:03:08.29,0:03:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbeknownst to him, the boy’s \Nkarma spiraled further out of control.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:12.42,0:03:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He had turned into a karma demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:15.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,業魔へと変わっていった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:20.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,業魔は\Nこの世に存在してはいけない
Dialogue: 9,0:03:16.75,0:03:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Karma demons ought not to walk this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:27.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,業魔は ひっそりと湖に姿を消した
Dialogue: 9,0:03:22.72,0:03:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He quietly walked his body to the bottom of a lake.{rep}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:31.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこにいるの？
Dialogue: 9,0:03:29.98,0:03:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:39.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早季…
Dialogue: 9,0:03:38.32,0:03:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Saki.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:41.36,0:03:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:43.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな所で何してるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:45.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分からない
Dialogue: 9,0:03:44.28,0:03:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:49.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今… 私 どこにいるの？
Dialogue: 9,0:03:46.28,0:03:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Where… am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.57,0:03:58.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,瞬… 瞬…
Dialogue: 9,0:03:54.50,0:03:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun… Shun…
Dialogue: 9,0:03:58.21,0:03:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.54,0:04:00.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,瞬！
Dialogue: 9,0:04:00.13,0:04:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn’t be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.56,0:04:02.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな所に来ちゃダメだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:12.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帰れ…
Dialogue: 9,0:04:10.64,0:04:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:16.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イヤよ！ うっ…
Dialogue: 9,0:04:13.02,0:04:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:24.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何が起きてるの？\N教えてくれなきゃ 私
Dialogue: 9,0:04:21.65,0:04:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:23.32,0:04:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I won’t budge until you tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:27.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここを動かないからね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:32.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早季…
Dialogue: 9,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Saki…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:35.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は 瞬を…
Dialogue: 9,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I… Shun…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:40.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,瞬に… 瞬…
Dialogue: 9,0:04:36.00,0:04:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun… Shun…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:44.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私 殺されそうになったんだから
Dialogue: 9,0:04:40.92,0:04:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was almost killed…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:58.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,猫に会ったのか
Dialogue: 9,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You met a cat?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:58.52,0:04:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:00.53,0:05:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your charm saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:04.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも 瞬にもらった\Nおまじないのおかげで助かったの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:07.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも たぶん もう１匹いる
Dialogue: 9,0:05:04.74,0:05:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think there’s another cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:13.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10分だけだ
Dialogue: 9,0:05:11.70,0:05:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten minutes.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:13.33,0:05:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stay here for ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:16.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10分間だけ ここにいていい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:20.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その間に できるだけの説明はする
Dialogue: 9,0:05:16.62,0:05:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll explain as much as I can in that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:29.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これ 瞬がやってるの？
Dialogue: 9,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this your doing?{Are you doing this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:35.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お面…
Dialogue: 9,0:05:33.60,0:05:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask…
Dialogue: 9,0:05:39.23,0:05:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:41.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,瞬…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:52.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,入ろう
Dialogue: 9,0:05:51.37,0:05:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:10.47,0:06:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:12.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10分間…
Dialogue: 9,0:06:15.31,0:06:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I can keep it under control for that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:18.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それくらいなら抑えられる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:32.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかたないんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:06:30.78,0:06:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:40.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっとの間だけ 我慢して
Dialogue: 9,0:06:37.08,0:06:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please bear with them for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:46.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのお面 取ってよ 何だか…
Dialogue: 9,0:06:44.55,0:06:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Take off that mask.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:46.26,0:06:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s so—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.56,0:06:48.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメだ
Dialogue: 9,0:06:47.09,0:06:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:55.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時間がない
Dialogue: 9,0:06:54.06,0:06:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.55,0:06:57.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何から話したらいいのかな
Dialogue: 9,0:06:56.14,0:06:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should I start?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:06:59.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,瞬 一体 何が…
Dialogue: 9,0:06:57.93,0:07:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s going on, Shun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:05.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全ての問題は\N人間の心から来るんだよ
Dialogue: 9,0:07:00.65,0:07:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All problems stem from the human heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:09.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間の心のうち
Dialogue: 9,0:07:07.86,0:07:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Our conscious self is just the tip of the iceberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:13.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,意識というのは\N氷山の一角にすぎない
Dialogue: 9,0:07:13.53,0:07:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The subconscious below the water is greater beyond comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:15.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,水面下にある無意識の方が
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:18.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はるかに広大なんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:07:20.54,0:07:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s not what I want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:22.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違うの！ そんな話じゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:26.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,瞬に何が起きたのか教えてよ！
Dialogue: 9,0:07:23.08,0:07:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me what’s happening to you!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:27.34,0:07:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s what I am talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:30.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを今 説明してるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:33.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間は どうやっても
Dialogue: 9,0:07:32.59,0:07:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite our best efforts, we humans cannot fully control our thoughts and feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:37.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分の心を\N完全に制御することはできない
Dialogue: 9,0:07:37.43,0:07:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Our subconscious, in particular, is rife with the unpredictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:42.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,特に無意識の中では\N思ってもみないことが起きている
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:53.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは呪力において\N最も顕著にあらわれるんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:07:48.69,0:07:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Cantus is the most tangible manifestation of this.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:54.41,0:08:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In the case of physical actions, there are multiple stages between the inception deep down and the eventual effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:56.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,物理的な行動を起こす場合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:59.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心に思い描いたことが\N実際に起きるまでは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:02.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくつかの段階がある
Dialogue: 9,0:08:02.37,0:08:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Although the original impetus is a product of our subconscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:06.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,動機は無意識から発していても\N行動に移す前には
Dialogue: 9,0:08:04.83,0:08:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,it needs to pass through our conscious thought before it can be realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:09.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,意識の領域を\N通過しなければならないから
Dialogue: 9,0:08:09.55,0:08:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Human reason can correct or altogether stop an action from being taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:11.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,理性によって\Nストップをかけられたり
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:14.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,修正したりすることができる
Dialogue: 9,0:08:14.18,0:08:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Cantus works differently, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:16.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど 呪力の場合
Dialogue: 9,0:08:16.55,0:08:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We can consider the inception and execution of an action to be practically simultaneous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:20.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思ったことが実現するまで\Nほとんど同時といってもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.59,0:08:24.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮に間違っていたとしても\N修正する暇がないんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:08:20.81,0:08:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it may be the wrong action, there is no time to correct it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:27.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,間違う… どういうこと？
Dialogue: 9,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:32.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イメージをちゃんと作らないと\N呪力は発動しないでしょう？
Dialogue: 9,0:08:27.90,0:08:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t using our Cantus tied to picturing very specific things?
Dialogue: 9,0:08:32.53,0:08:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Some mental images are clearly and consciously conceived,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:36.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのイメージにも\N明確に意識されているものと
Dialogue: 9,0:08:36.49,0:08:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,while others are shrouded in the darkness of the subconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:40.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無意識の闇に\N飲み込まれたままのものがある
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.57,0:08:45.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど 皆 分かっていない
Dialogue: 9,0:08:42.66,0:08:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody realizes this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:51.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,呪力は 暗示や真言を使って
Dialogue: 9,0:08:48.63,0:08:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We try to keep our Canti strictly \Ncontrolled through hypnosis and mantras.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:53.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,厳格に管理しようとしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:57.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でもね 無意識下に開いた出口から
Dialogue: 9,0:08:54.26,0:08:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the end, it always leaks through \Nthe holes opened by our subconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:09:00.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず漏出が起きるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:02.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,漏出…
Dialogue: 9,0:09:00.89,0:09:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaks through?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.58,0:09:05.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,呪力は常に漏れ出している
Dialogue: 9,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Canti are constantly leaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:08.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕らは ある意味では\N無意識の命ずるままに
Dialogue: 9,0:09:05.90,0:09:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In a sense, we are changing the world around us at the whim of our subconsciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:12.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,周囲の世界に\N変化をもたらし続けているんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:14.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな…
Dialogue: 9,0:09:13.57,0:09:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:17.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早季は\N八丁標が何のためにあると思う？
Dialogue: 9,0:09:14.70,0:09:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think the Holy Barrier is for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:19.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは…
Dialogue: 9,0:09:18.32,0:09:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 9,0:09:19.53,0:09:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think it’s there to protect us from unknown threats outside of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:21.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外からくる\N得体の知れないモノから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:24.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕たちを守るため？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:26.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうでしょう
Dialogue: 9,0:09:25.00,0:09:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t it?
Dialogue: 9,0:09:26.50,0:09:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:29.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違う 八丁標は外敵ではなく
Dialogue: 9,0:09:27.92,0:09:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Holy Barrier defends against \Ninternal threats, not external ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:32.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,内なる敵に対処するために\N作られたんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:09:32.46,0:09:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Internal threats?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:34.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,内なる… 敵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:37.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶えず漏出してる 僕たちの呪力だ
Dialogue: 9,0:09:35.42,0:09:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s our own, constantly leaking Cantus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:39.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪鬼にせよ 業魔にせよ
Dialogue: 9,0:09:38.30,0:09:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider fiends or karma demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:43.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 僕らにとって恐怖とは\N内からやってくるものなんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:09:40.35,0:09:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We ultimately fear what spawns from within us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:47.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もちろん 漏出している呪力は\Nごく微弱だから
Dialogue: 9,0:09:44.43,0:09:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the Canti that leaks out is feeble and won’t ravage the world overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:50.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一朝一夕に\Nどうかなるものじゃない
Dialogue: 9,0:09:50.36,0:09:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But if our thoughts and ideas continue to amass and interfere with each other for an extended period of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:54.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも長期間お互いの思念に\N干渉 蓄積し続ければ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.58,0:09:56.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その影響は計り知れない
Dialogue: 9,0:09:55.36,0:09:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,then there is no predicting the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:10:01.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから どうしても\Nそれを外に向けてやる必要がある
Dialogue: 9,0:09:57.24,0:10:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This means there is a need to direct it outwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.59,0:10:05.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕らは幼い頃から繰り返し
Dialogue: 9,0:10:03.29,0:10:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Since our childhood, we’ve been \Nconditioned to fear the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.59,0:10:08.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外の世界に対する恐怖を\N刷り込まれてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:11.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど\N巨大な暗黒世界のイメージは
Dialogue: 9,0:10:09.21,0:10:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,However, an image of that dark, \Nboundless world also exists within us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:13.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕らの内にもある
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.56,0:10:15.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう１つの暗黒の宇宙である
Dialogue: 9,0:10:14.38,0:10:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It becomes one with the dark universe inside ourselves—our subconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:19.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無意識と\N同一化されるようになる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:23.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心の中で 無意識を\N外の世界と直結させることで
Dialogue: 9,0:10:19.80,0:10:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,By linking our subconscious to the outside world,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:27.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,漏出を八丁標の外へと導くんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:10:23.89,0:10:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,we direct such leakages outside the Holy Barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:30.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,八丁標は 僕らの｢みそぎ｣のための
Dialogue: 9,0:10:28.23,0:10:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The Holy Barrier is like a charm required for our purification.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:33.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おまじないみたいなものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.58,0:10:38.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ その外へ出された呪力は\Nどうなるの？
Dialogue: 9,0:10:34.07,0:10:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What does the Cantus do outside the barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:40.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ミノシロの祖先は
Dialogue: 9,0:10:38.99,0:10:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The minoshiro’s ancestor is most likely a sea slug.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:43.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おそらく\N海にいる ミノウミウシだろうけど
Dialogue: 9,0:10:44.45,0:10:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying the leakage of our Canti created the minoshiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:48.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私たちから漏出した呪力が\Nミノシロを作ったってこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:51.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ミノシロだけじゃない\Nトラバサミも
Dialogue: 9,0:10:49.04,0:10:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only the minoshiro.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:50.58,0:10:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Tigercrabs and haythatchers as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.59,0:10:54.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カヤノスヅクリだってそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:59.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが正しいかどうか\N私には分からない
Dialogue: 9,0:10:55.00,0:10:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t know if you’re correct or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:01.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 9,0:10:59.63,0:11:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:04.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも 正直 言ってどうでもいい
Dialogue: 9,0:11:01.89,0:11:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But I really don’t think it matters either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.57,0:11:08.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が知りたいのは…
Dialogue: 9,0:11:05.35,0:11:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to know…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:12.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が… 知りたいのは
Dialogue: 9,0:11:08.89,0:11:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to know what’s happening to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.59,0:11:16.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,瞬の身に\N何が起きたかってことだけなの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.59,0:11:37.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫 すばるだよ
Dialogue: 9,0:11:34.21,0:11:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:35.54,0:11:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:43.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おいで
Dialogue: 9,0:11:41.88,0:11:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:58.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何も… 僕は 本当に…
Dialogue: 9,0:11:55.81,0:11:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,None of this… I really…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:00.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何もしたくなかったんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:11:59.19,0:12:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn’t want to do any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:16.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かるだろう？
Dialogue: 9,0:12:15.08,0:12:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand now?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:16.59,0:12:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All this is the result of what’s happening to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:20.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが\N僕に起きたことの結果なんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:23.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,呪力の漏出が止まらないんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:12:20.88,0:12:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My Cantus just won’t stop escaping.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:23.47,0:12:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s also growing in intensity, and \NI’m less and less able to control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:28.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それも どんどん激しく\N制御不能になりつつある
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:36.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無意識の暴走により\N呪力の異常漏出が起きて
Dialogue: 9,0:12:30.81,0:12:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My subconsciousness has gone out of control, resulting in extreme leakages of my Cantus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.59,0:12:41.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,周囲のもの 全てが\N破壊的な影響を受け
Dialogue: 9,0:12:36.69,0:12:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Under its destructive effects, \Neverything around me is warped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:43.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,異形化してしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.60,0:12:47.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが\N橋本･アッペルバウム症候群だ
Dialogue: 9,0:12:44.61,0:12:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Hashimoto-Appelbaum syndrome.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:54.58,0:12:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:56.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕は…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:58.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,業魔になった
Dialogue: 9,0:12:56.83,0:12:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,…turned into a karma demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:08.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな ウソよ…
Dialogue: 9,0:13:06.59,0:13:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That can’t be…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.63,0:13:11.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残念ながら 本当だ
Dialogue: 9,0:13:09.05,0:13:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s sad but true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.62,0:13:20.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここにある本は
Dialogue: 9,0:13:19.52,0:13:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All these books contain knowledge that was \Nsupposed to have been consigned to oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:24.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,永遠に葬り去るべき知識と\Nされているものばかりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:28.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早季のお母さんが\N特別に貸してくれた
Dialogue: 9,0:13:25.07,0:13:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother went out of her way to lend them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:30.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お母さんが…？
Dialogue: 9,0:13:29.16,0:13:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:33.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,業魔化という現象について\N知識を得るには
Dialogue: 9,0:13:31.20,0:13:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Reading these books is the only way to learn \Nwhat changing into a karma demon is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:35.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これを読む以外にない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:38.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが 分かっている全てなんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:13:36.08,0:13:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:44.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕は自分自身の記録を付けている
Dialogue: 9,0:13:42.59,0:13:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m writing down my own experience too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:49.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やがては\Nいちばん新しい症例として…
Dialogue: 9,0:13:45.59,0:13:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I’m merely the most recent case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:53.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕の名前も ここに加わることに
Dialogue: 9,0:13:50.55,0:13:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to add my name to the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:14:01.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなこと言わないでよ
Dialogue: 9,0:13:59.02,0:14:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:05.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それより どうすれば瞬は治るの？
Dialogue: 9,0:14:03.15,0:14:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any way we can reverse this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:09.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,呪力を封印することは\Nできないの？
Dialogue: 9,0:14:06.90,0:14:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Can’t we seal your Cantus?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:14.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無瞋上人に\N施術をしてもらったんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:14:10.66,0:14:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Head Priest Mushin tried that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.63,0:14:21.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕の呪力は\N蓋が壊れたような状態で…
Dialogue: 9,0:14:18.29,0:14:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My Cantus is like something with a broken lid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:23.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,止めることは
Dialogue: 9,0:14:22.04,0:14:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s unlikely that anything can hold it back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.64,0:14:26.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できないらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:32.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それって もしかして…
Dialogue: 9,0:14:30.39,0:14:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:38.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が間違ったやり方で\N瞬の呪力を復活させたから
Dialogue: 9,0:14:34.93,0:14:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,…I didn’t restore your Cantus correctly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:41.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早季のせいじゃない！
Dialogue: 9,0:14:38.85,0:14:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s not your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:43.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そろそろ帰った方がいい
Dialogue: 9,0:14:41.73,0:14:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:47.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕は今 ありったけの呪力を\Nハチ玉に向けることで
Dialogue: 9,0:14:44.07,0:14:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m focusing all my Cantus on the wasp balls right now so that it doesn’t affect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:50.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君に影響が及ぶのを防いでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:52.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,集中力が鈍ると
Dialogue: 9,0:14:51.16,0:14:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Once my concentration wanes, I can’t say when it will become uncontrollable again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつ暴走が始まるか分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:58.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イヤ！ 帰らない 一緒にいたい
Dialogue: 9,0:14:55.29,0:14:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I won’t go!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:57.66,0:14:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be with you!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:58.62,0:14:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Saki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:01.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早季… 僕は このために
Dialogue: 9,0:15:00.21,0:15:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My condition has already caused the death of my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:04.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,両親を死なせてしまった
Dialogue: 9,0:15:06.30,0:15:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So please go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:08.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから帰ってくれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:10.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これ以上 僕のために
Dialogue: 9,0:15:09.01,0:15:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t want anyone else I love to die in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:13.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,愛する人が死ぬのは\N見たくないんだ！
Dialogue: 9,0:15:16.43,0:15:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:18.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私には…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:21.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,瞬は救えない
Dialogue: 9,0:15:19.31,0:15:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,…can’t save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:27.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私には 何もできない！
Dialogue: 9,0:15:24.73,0:15:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t do anything!
Dialogue: 9,0:15:49.55,0:15:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:51.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,瞬…
Dialogue: 9,0:15:51.63,0:15:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.64,0:15:54.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私に 何かしてほしいことは？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:21.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早季 やめろ！
Dialogue: 9,0:16:20.29,0:16:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Saki, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:46.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめて…
Dialogue: 9,0:16:44.81,0:16:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:10.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,瞬…
Dialogue: 9,0:17:09.42,0:17:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun!
Dialogue: 9,0:17:10.59,0:17:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru tried to rescue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:13.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すばるは 僕を助けようとしたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:17.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことをしても\N何にもならないのに
Dialogue: 9,0:17:14.47,0:17:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite how futile it was…{i’m pretty sure this line is referring to subaru’s heroic act, but i’d seek confirmation from the novel}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:20.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何度も置いて行こうとしたんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:17:18.68,0:17:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to leave him behind many, many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:23.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも どうしても付いてくる
Dialogue: 9,0:17:21.22,0:17:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, he followed me every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:29.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当は 僕の方が\N寂しかったのかもしれない
Dialogue: 9,0:17:26.77,0:17:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I was the lonely one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.66,0:17:31.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すばるがいなくなったら
Dialogue: 9,0:17:30.11,0:17:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I’d be all alone without Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:34.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひとりぼっちになっちゃうから…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:38.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの猫だって\N別に悪くなかったんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:17:35.15,0:17:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s not the cat’s fault either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:40.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ 命令どおり 僕を
Dialogue: 9,0:17:39.28,0:17:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s here simply because it was ordered to end my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.63,0:17:43.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕の始末をつけに来た
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:45.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.64,0:17:49.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕がやるべきことを決断する\Nタイミングが遅かった
Dialogue: 9,0:17:45.96,0:17:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve taken too long to decide on what I should’ve done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:51.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 9,0:17:50.21,0:17:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:55.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと早く\N決着をつけるべきだった
Dialogue: 9,0:17:53.09,0:17:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have ended this much sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.65,0:17:59.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕がずるずると引き伸ばしたから
Dialogue: 9,0:17:57.05,0:17:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn’t been so indecisive,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:02.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すばるを…
Dialogue: 9,0:18:00.72,0:18:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru wouldn’t have had to suffer like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:04.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな目にあわせちゃった…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.66,0:18:11.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たくさんの錠剤が入った瓶を
Dialogue: 9,0:18:08.90,0:18:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I was given a bottle of pills before I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:14.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここへ来る直前にもらったんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:18:11.77,0:18:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A combination of various types of poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:17.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いろんな種類の\N毒の詰合せなんだよ
Dialogue: 9,0:18:15.07,0:18:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t you think it’s a cruel parting gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:20.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひどい せん別だと思わないか
Dialogue: 9,0:18:18.74,0:18:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m glad you didn’t take any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:23.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなの 飲まなくてよかったわ
Dialogue: 9,0:18:21.41,0:18:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You should’ve just thrown them all away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:25.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,捨てちゃえばいいのに
Dialogue: 9,0:18:23.79,0:18:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I took them all.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:25.08,0:18:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They just didn’t work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:29.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飲んだよ\Nだけど 効かなかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:34.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分子性の毒は\N簡単に変性してしまうらしいね
Dialogue: 9,0:18:30.67,0:18:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it’s easy to detoxify poisons on a molecular level.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:37.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死にたくないという無意識が
Dialogue: 9,0:18:35.34,0:18:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My subconscious desire to survive \Nmust’ve altered the elements themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:40.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,元素まで\N変換してしまったのかもしれない
Dialogue: 9,0:18:50.60,0:18:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it’s coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:52.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来るみたいだ
Dialogue: 9,0:18:52.36,0:18:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.64,0:18:54.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何が…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.64,0:18:58.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早く ここを出るんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:18:56.44,0:18:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:07.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕の家が\N大地に飲み込まれた時と同じだ
Dialogue: 9,0:19:03.83,0:19:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The same happened when my \Nhome was swallowed by the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:09.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,笑っちゃうだろう
Dialogue: 9,0:19:08.21,0:19:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t it funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:11.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,祝霊にそっくりだから
Dialogue: 9,0:19:09.75,0:19:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s just like the Spirit of Blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.66,0:19:14.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちは\N祝福を与えてくれるどころか
Dialogue: 9,0:19:12.21,0:19:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet instead of blessing you, all it brings is death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.66,0:19:16.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死の使いだけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:21.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早く！
Dialogue: 9,0:19:19.84,0:19:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:27.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度こそ 終わりにするよ
Dialogue: 9,0:19:26.10,0:19:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll put an end to it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:30.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうたくさんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:19:29.06,0:19:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:39.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早季…
Dialogue: 9,0:19:37.69,0:19:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Saki…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:43.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ずっと好きだった
Dialogue: 9,0:19:40.49,0:19:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve always loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:50.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さようなら…
Dialogue: 9,0:19:48.29,0:19:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:23.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,瞬～！
Dialogue: 9,0:20:21.61,0:20:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:38.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は… 生きなければならない
Dialogue: 9,0:20:34.75,0:20:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to stay alive.
